    "narrativeArc": "The video analyzes why women are attracted to men who display indifference, contrasting it with traditional courtship. It breaks down three psychological 'addiction triggers': the variable reward system (inconsistent attention creates obsession), role reversal (making the woman chase), and the ego hook (challenging her self-image). Through minimalist stick figure animations and text, it illustrates how a man's perceived indifference creates doubt, projects higher value, and leads to emotional investment, ultimately making him unforgettable. The video concludes by advocating for projecting power through detachment rather than seeking approval."
